import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
const Navbar = () => {
    return ( <
        header >
        <
        div className = "container" >
        <
        Link to = "/" >
        <
        h1 > Workout BUBDY < /h1> < /
        Link >
        <
        nav >
        <
        div >
        <
        Link to = "/login" > Login < /Link> <
        Link to = "/signup" > Signup < /Link>

        <
        /div> <
        /nav>  <
        /div> < /
        header >
    )
}
export default Navbar
